    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. Validation results demonstrate RH index predictions within acceptance criteria across all five operating points. The assessment team reviewed the patch-level difference between the validation build (ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2) and the production build (ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7) and concluded, based on vendor release notes, that no solver-relevant changes were introduced. The team accepted the validation evidence as applicable to the production model without re-executing the validation suite under the released binary. Overall credibility assessment: ACCEPTED for COU1 at Medium assurance level.",
